      section.whatIs
      h3
          | So what is smartTips?
        p
          | smartTips is a jQuery plugin that finds  
          | words on your webpage that you define. 
          | Then it wraps them in a span with a class of .smartTip. 
          | When you hover over the span it will pop out a tooltip with the corresponding text.
        p
          | How cool is that?
      section.howItWorks
        h3
          | How does it work?
        p
          | It's simple.
          | To get started, all you have to do is:
          ol
            li get the smartTips repo
            li include the smartTips.js file in your project
            li open the smartTips.js file
            li enter 'word' : 'definition' under 'var definitions'
            li style the classes .smartTip and .tooltip 
            li (optional) use the use the files in the the css folder to get started quickly 
        p
          | Here are the definitions I used for this demo page.
